headline: Hormel Foods Releases 2024 Global Impact Report
summary: Hormel Foods Corporation, a Fortune 500 global branded food company, today shared its 19th annual Global Impact Report. The report, available online, provides fiscal year 2024 progress through the lens of Good Feeds Us All, the company's next-generation global impact framework.
